### --- REVIEWS ---

### ════════════════════════════════════════
### Submit review for Apache Burger
### ════════════════════════════════════════
### 🔄 UPDATED LINE:
###    "visit_id": "1fa97363-11e2-4e8b-9247-243a859742a7", (or whatever ID from first successful visit)
###    ❌ Was: "visit_id": "REPLACE_WITH_VISIT_ID_FROM_FIRST_SUCCESSFUL_VISIT",
### ════════════════════════════════════════
POST http://localhost:3001/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visit_id": "1fa97363-11e2-4e8b-9247-243a859742a7",
  "user_id": "aaaa1111-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeee11111111",
  "restaurant_id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "taste_rating": 5,
  "value_rating": 4,
  "vibe_rating": 4,
  "wow_rating": 5,
  "comment": "Unreal smash burger. The chipotle aioli is addictive.",
  "would_return": true
}

