### Get reviews for Apache Burger
### Should return: array of reviews with ratings and comments
GET http://localhost:3001/api/reviews/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

### --- LEADERBOARD ---

### Get restaurant rankings
### Should return: ranked list with avg ratings, visit counts, would-return %
GET http://localhost:3001/api/leaderboard

### --- LOYALTY ---

### Get loyalty card for Test Explorer
### Should return: stamps_earned, tier_reached, visited_restaurant_ids, tiers with unlocked status
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/aaaa1111-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeee11111111/loyalty

### Get loyalty card for user with no visits
### Should return: stamps_earned: 0, all tiers unlocked: false
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/aaaa3333-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeee33333333/loyalty

### Get loyalty card with invalid UUID
### Should return: 400 with "Invalid user ID" message
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/not-a-uuid/loyalty
